title: SpaceX launches Starlink satellites into orbit on 100th Falcon 9 flight from Florida in 2025 (video)
description: A SpaceX Falcon 9 rocket carrying 29 Starlink satellites lifted off from Space Launch Complex 40 at Cape Canaveral Space Force Station in Florida on Monday, Dec. 15, 2025.
